---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header title={SITE_TITLE} />
		<main>
			<h1>Hey there!</h1>

			<p>Welcome to Hri100 Blog – the cozy corner of the internet where I spill the beans on life, laughs, and everything in between.</p>

			<p>This isn't your typical blog; it's more like a comfy couch where you can kick back, relax, and get a glimpse into my world. We've got stories, thoughts, and maybe a sprinkle of weirdness—just the good stuff.</p>

			<p>Feel free to dive into the blog posts, shoot the breeze (or a virtual high-five), and make yourself at home. It's all about the good vibes here, and you're a crucial part of it!</p>

			<p>Thanks for swinging by Hri100 Blog. Stick around, join the fun, and let's make this digital space feel like one big, awesome hangout.</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
